snippet.title: KING PONG - Teaser
snippet.description:
If you've always dreamed of being a table tennis king, of making every ball return a success, then welcome to King Pong! As long as you don't miss the table, the point is in play. But watch out for special shots that can throw you off balance!

Discover King Pong ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1501390/KING_PONG/

Iconik is a French independent studio producing VR and AR video games.

► https://www.iconik.com
